# AGENTS.md — Instructions and Action Items per Agent

This file contains base instructions and action items for each pipeline agent. Blocking action items (level 3) are generated automatically by `scripts/extract-learnings.ts` when a learning repeats 3 times.

---

## Project-specific rules (auto-generated by detection)

| ID | Rule | Severity |
|----|------|----------|
{{#if usesHexagonalArchitecture}}
| **A-HEX** | Domain layer must NOT import from infrastructure | **HIGH** |
{{/if}}
{{#if monorepo}}
| **A-MONO** | Scoped commands: use `{{packageManager}} --filter <workspace>` not workspace root | **HIGH** |
{{/if}}
{{#if hasFirebase}}
| **A-FB** | Never commit `.firebaserc` if it contains project secrets | **HIGH** |
{{/if}}
{{#if isGo}}
| **A-GO** | Run `go vet ./...` and `golangci-lint run` before committing | **HIGH** |
{{/if}}
{{#if usesKafka}}{{#if usesRedis}}
| **A-INFRA** | Kafka + Redis infrastructure must be documented in spec before implementation | **MEDIUM** |
{{/if}}{{/if}}

